1385
01:46:59,306 --> 01:47:00,141
Where are you going?

1386
01:47:00,145 --> 01:47:02,377
He said he's got pills.
Maybe they're in the car.

1387
01:47:34,968 --> 01:47:38,826
Can you hear me?
Open your mouth. Open!

1388
01:47:55,093 --> 01:47:58,117
Mister! Get up!
Can you hear me?

1389
01:48:01,559 --> 01:48:04,166
Oh, God! Oh, God!

1390
01:48:05,939 --> 01:48:08,338
You better now?
You feeling better?

1391
01:48:11,362 --> 01:48:15,220
Breathe! Breathe!
You better, now?

1392
01:48:29,924 --> 01:48:30,966
Don't worry, he's better.

1393
01:48:30,967 --> 01:48:32,740
